  "instructions": [
    "Blanch the bulgur in boiling water for 5 minutes, then drain and set aside.",
    "In a large bowl, combine the lemon and lime juice, tabasco sauce, and namul blanch seasoning.",
    "Add the pine nuts, salt, and black pepper to the bowl and stir to combine.",
    "Stir in the chopped parsley and mint.",
    "Add the blanched bulgur to the bowl and stir until well combined.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "Serve the tabbouleh fatteh cold, garnished with additional parsley and mint if desired.",
    "Pair with naan or pita bread for a satisfying crunch and a side of yogurt or raita for a cooling contrast."
